data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. Welcome to this remarkable 4 bedroom 3 bath home with over 3103 sqft. that offers an expansive living space and countless possibilities. For the DIY Professional, this is the perfect home to make your own. Don't let this incredible opportunity slip away – it's time to make this your own!As you step inside, you'll immediately appreciate the abundance of room that this home provides. The spacious living area is perfect for entertaining friends and family or simply unwinding after a long day. Its' open layout allows for seamless flow and effortless interaction between all the main rooms of the home.The kitchen is ready for its make over. With your own touch on the new kitchen, you have a chance to create your own space with your design. A sliding window offers access to the Air conditioned Florida Room off of both the living room and great room.With four bedrooms, this home ensures everyone has their own private little haven. Escape to the owners suite, which features a spacious layout and an en-suite bathroom with his and her walk in closets for your utmost convenience and relaxation.One of the standout features of this property is the large backyard, fully fenced off for your privacy and security. It presents an inviting outdoor space where you can host gatherings, enjoy outdoor activities, or simply bask in the serenity of nature.Located in a Christina Woods community, this home offers proximity to schools, shopping centers, parks, and other amenities. The convenient location ensures you have everything you need within reach.Don't let this incredible opportunity slip through your fingers. Take the leap and make this expansive 4 bedroom home yours today. Schedule a viewing now and envision the endless possibilities this property holds for you and your loved ones!
